channel.title: Why is RSC dying slow
channel.description:
iv played rsc servers for while now and it seems to me like its dying slow...
am i the only one who sees this shit?
i remember few years back i used to run to library to play rsc thats when it was fun just knowing ur gonna get on and rape some ass in wild.. looting in wild waiting for drops to pop up, just dying to get that rune when it pops up..getting excited when ur bout to get a kill.. GOOD TIMES.
then rs2 comes out, ...................................................then what
